sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor R as Retailer
    actor B as Brand
    actor M as Model Provider
    participant FE as Web dApp
    participant BE as Backend (BFF)
    participant SE as Seal
    participant WA as Walrus
    participant SUI as Sui (Tatum RPC)

    Note over R,SUI: Flow A — 上傳 & 發行 Dataset
    R->>FE: 上傳匿名化 CSV
    FE->>BE: 送檔
    BE->>SE: seal_encrypt(plaintext)
    SE-->>BE: encryptedObject
    BE->>WA: writeBlob(encrypted) → blobId
    BE->>SUI: register_dataset(blobId, seal_inner_id, ...)
    SUI-->>FE: DatasetRegistered(dataset_id)

    Note over B,SUI: Flow B — 購買使用權 & 訓練
    B->>FE: 選多家 dataset 建 campaign
    FE->>SUI: create_campaign(dataset_ids, provider)
    B->>SUI: fund_campaign(Coin<T>) → status=Active
    SUI->>SUI: issue_access_ticket() → 給 provider
    M->>BE: 觸發訓練
    BE->>SE: SessionKey + seal_approve(ticket) → key shares
    BE->>WA: readBlob(blobId) → 解密
    BE->>BE: 訓練 → 報表
    BE->>WA: writeBlob(report) → report_blob_id
    M->>SUI: settle_campaign(ProviderCap, hash, report_blob_id)
    SUI->>SUI: 按 rev_weights 拆 budget → 各 owner
    SUI-->>FE: CampaignSettled

    Note over R,SUI: Flow C — 供應者查收益
    R->>FE: 開儀表板
    FE->>SUI: 拉 UsageRecord
    FE->>WA: readBlob(report) 重算驗證 hash
